""" Test intialising with string of lattice parameters """
self.Crystal = readcoords.Crystal(cell=str(self.cell['a']) + ' ' + str(self
    .cell['b']) + ' ' + str(self.cell['c']) + ' ' + str(self.cell['alp']) +
    ' ' + str(self.cell['bet']) + ' ' + str(self.cell['gam']), atoms=None,
    atomtypes=None)
self.assertEqual(self.Crystal.cell, self.cell)
